Class IdListResponse

  • java.lang.Object

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    @Preamble(description="Paginated response corresponding to one page of ids.")
public class IdListResponse
extends AbstractListResponse<java.lang.String>
    Most listing operations are paginated and respond with truncated results. This object comprises the information related to one page of ids.
